==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blinder
<hw>Blind"er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who, or that which, blinds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Saddlery)</fld> <def>One of the leather screens on
a bridle, to hinder a horse from seeing objects at the side; a
blinker.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blindfish</ent>⟦br⟧
